2 crazy characters with great sense of fashion ❤️‍🔥
Had a lot of fun working on this one and I couldn’t be happier with the result. Might be one of my best drawings yet, love how the boots turned out. 
I also made a video about this one and I’m really proud of it, make sure to check it it out aswell 🤝
Anyway, thank you so much for the crazy support and hope you like this one as much as I do!

node.text:
I tried oil painting for the first time🎨

This is also my first time trying to paint a realistic portrait and I’m so happy with the result! Can’t wait to start working on more oil paintings 🤝

Also painted a small landscape and an eye to practice before doing the portrait, hope you like them as well!

Don’t forget to watch the video about this one on Yt! One of my favorites yet

What do you think about this one?

node.text:
I made an animation in 24 different styles!

I finally worked on another animation since the last one I made in 2020 and I’m super proud of the result!🤝
For this one I used @clipstudioofficial ‘s epic painting/animation software and a Wacom Cintiq 16!

Had a lot of fun animating and can’t wait to start working on another one!
Don’t forget to watch the video about it on YouTube ✨(very epic)✨

Hope you like it as much as I do!
.
PS: big thanks to @clipstudioofficial for making this possible, make sure to give it a try! You won’t regret it 
.
.
